channel.title: Dr. Gameshow
channel.description: Jo Firestone and Manolo Moreno play original game shows sent in by listeners with their comedian friends and listener call-ins. Listen as Jo and Manolo struggle through these outrageous games submitted by people all over the world, from New Jersey to Pakistan. This cult favorite radio show is now on Earwolf.
